docs Update
    Pure state reducer. Takes the current count and an action type.
    The flow wiring routes events to the correct handler by port name,
    so Update only needs to apply the action.
done

func Update
    take count as long
    take type as text
    emit count as long
body
    case type
        when "inc"
            emit count + 1
        when "dec"
            emit count - 1
        else
            emit count
    done
done

test Update
    it "increments"
        result = Update(0, "inc")
        must result == 1
    done
    it "decrements"
        result = Update(5, "dec")
        must result == 4
    done
    it "passes through unknown type"
        result = Update(3, "other")
        must result == 3
    done
done
